sequenceDiagram
  actor Student
  participant Web as React Web Client
  participant API as TutorController
  participant Auth as AuthGuard
  participant Tutor as TutorService
  participant Lesson as LessonService
  participant Profile as StudentProfileService
  participant Background as BackgroundAiService
  participant Knowledge as KnowledgeService
  participant DB as SQLite
  participant AIModel as AiModelService
  participant Policy as AiOperationPolicyService
  participant Usage as UsageService
  participant OpenAI as OpenAI-backed model provider

  Student->>Web: Type prompt or use speech recognition
  Web->>API: POST /tutor/message with lessonType
  API->>Auth: Validate session cookie
  Auth-->>API: Authenticated user
  API->>Tutor: answerMessage(user, message, source, lessonType)
  Tutor->>Lesson: beginTurn(userId, conversationId, lessonType)
  Lesson->>DB: Upsert lesson_sessions and compute limits
  DB-->>Lesson: Recent progress/regression rows
  Lesson-->>Tutor: Lesson lifecycle and strategy signal
  alt Hard learning limit reached
    Tutor->>DB: Insert local stop tutor_turn
    Tutor-->>API: TutorAnswer with stop lifecycle
    API-->>Web: Stop response and usage snapshot
  else Tutor may continue
  Tutor->>Profile: getTutorContext(userId)
  Profile->>DB: Read student_profiles
  DB-->>Profile: Profile summary and strategy
  Profile-->>Tutor: Tutor profile context
  Tutor->>Knowledge: getActiveVectorStoreIds()
  Knowledge->>DB: Read knowledge_files when env ids absent
  Knowledge-->>Tutor: Vector store ids
  Tutor->>AIModel: Create tutor operation response with lifecycle, profile context, lesson type, usage context, and optional file_search
  AIModel->>Policy: Resolve tutorAnswer or tutorAnswerWithRag policy
  Policy-->>AIModel: Role, model, metadata, optional service tier
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Responses API request
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: Structured tutor JSON blocks and citations
  AIModel->>Usage: Record operation usage when usage context exists
  Usage->>DB: Insert ai_usage_ledger
  AIModel-->>Tutor: Provider response
  Tutor->>Lesson: completeTurn(goalStatus, answer shape)
  Lesson->>DB: Update lesson_sessions and insert lesson_effectiveness_signals
  Tutor->>DB: Insert tutor_turn with lesson_type
  Tutor->>Background: enqueueTutorTurnWork()
  alt Background batching enabled
    Background->>DB: Insert background_learning_observations with lesson_type
    Background->>DB: Schedule or reschedule learning_window_analysis job
  else Legacy background mode
    Background->>DB: Insert per-turn background_ai_jobs
  end
  Tutor->>Usage: Read lesson/day usage snapshot
  Usage->>DB: Summarize ai_usage_ledger
  Tutor-->>API: TutorAnswer with lesson lifecycle, usage, and ordered blocks
  API-->>Web: Lesson type, lifecycle, usage, text, task, example, image blocks, citations
  Web->>API: GET /usage/me/summary
  API->>Usage: getUserSummary(userId, lessonSessionId)
  Usage->>DB: Read ai_usage_ledger for signed-in user
  API-->>Web: Usage summary for usage bar
  end
  Note over Background,AIModel: Later drain groups stored observations by window size, idle timeout, or quality trigger
  Background->>DB: Recover stale queued observations and running jobs
  Background->>DB: Read pending observations and job queue
  Background->>DB: Mark selected observations queued
  Background->>AIModel: Learning-window operation with optional prompt cache key
  AIModel->>Policy: Resolve backgroundLearningWindow policy
  Policy-->>AIModel: Background role, model, optional service tier
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Responses API request
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: Learning-window JSON
  AIModel->>Usage: Record background operation usage
  Usage->>DB: Insert ai_usage_ledger
  AIModel-->>Background: Parsed model response
  Background->>DB: Store analysis window, signals, session summaries, skill progress, processed observations
  alt Window analysis fails
    Background->>DB: Return claimed observations to pending
  end
  opt Profile refresh interval reached
    Background->>AIModel: Combined profile/strategy refresh operation
    AIModel->>Policy: Resolve backgroundProfileStrategyRefresh policy
    Policy-->>AIModel: Background role, model, optional service tier
    AIModel->>OpenAI: Responses API request
    OpenAI-->>AIModel: Profile and strategy patch JSON
    AIModel-->>Background: Parsed model response
    Background->>DB: Update student_profiles
  end
  opt Image block present
    Student->>Web: Request diagram from image block
    Web->>API: POST /tutor/image
    API->>Tutor: generateImage(prompt, context, lessonSessionId)
    Tutor->>AIModel: Generate tutorImage operation PNG
    AIModel->>Policy: Resolve tutorImage policy
    Policy-->>AIModel: Image role and model
    AIModel->>OpenAI: Images API request
    OpenAI-->>AIModel: Base64 image
    AIModel->>Usage: Record image usage
    Usage->>DB: Insert ai_usage_ledger
    AIModel-->>Tutor: Image response
    Tutor-->>API: Data URL and usage snapshot
    API-->>Web: Render generated image and refresh usage
  end
